elements.html: Before we dive into the lifecycle stages of your board-building process, we must start with you! What are you all about, and why?

elements.html: No one else can tell you what your ‚Äúwhy‚Äù or your purpose is; this is intrinsic. Others can help you uncover your why, and they can guide you on your journey, but you have to take the first steps.

elements.name: What is something that makes you jump out of bed in the morning, you get so excited about this concept or activity?
